{"word":"G3375 - μήν - mḗn - mane - + surely","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">μήν</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">mḗn</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">mane</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">+ surely</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>NA / Not Available</span>"},{"paragraph":"நிச்சயமாக - எச்சம்"},{"paragraph":"verily, certainly, truly"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>A stronger form of <a href=\"#/G3303 - μέν - mén - men/3303\">G3303</a>; a particle of affirmation (only with <a href=\"#/G2229 - ἦ - ē - ay/2229\">G2229</a>); <i>assuredly:</i> - + surely.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}